cast.name: 潘妮拉·奥古斯特 Pernilla August

director.name: 詹姆斯·维拉斯克斯 James Velasquez

this_title: The Last Journey of the Vikings
introduction: Nearly 1,000 years ago, the Vikings left Scandinavia and settled across Europe - giving their name to Normandy along the way - before their Norman descendants seized the English throne at the Battle of Hastings in 1066. But what do we really know about them? By combining expert analysis with compelling drama, 'The Last Journey of the Vikings' (Swedish title: 'Vikingarnas sista resa') tells a new and often surprising story about this complex people.
